{"tid":694683,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】射擊之路，有你有我 Day215 8/6","createTime":"2018-06-08T14:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T17:10:18.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"46d54fb3bbf4d6d04f6c53a1b8e32fd4772452d5","tid":694683,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚10點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a1ee9cfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1a75f60d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"1600ac9e5cca0ca5dd401e480a4e6b14d5c6ddc5","tid":694683,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:17:19.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb174fdfeb9f567559932f72ea25f93eb3211f4","tid":694683,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270722091cd40f45f8100709a4fd8ab7d8bddb1c","tid":694